com.esri.mo2.cs.geod
Class Point3D

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.cs.geod.Point3D
public class Point3D
extends Object

A 3 dimensional point, having an x, y and z component. For performance reasons, it is not represent it by an interface. The x and y components can represent the easting and northing of a projected coordinate system respectively. The x and y components can represent the longitude and latitude of a geographic coordinate system respectively. Latitude and longitude are always in radians. When used with Ellipsoid, Point3D is either in meters or radians depending on its application (the method).
